  <title>tmux-&tmux-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      tmux is a terminal multiplexer that lets you switch easily between
      several programs in one terminal, detach them and reattach them to a
      different terminal.
    </para>

